meta.text: Extension does not affect operation of National Law in respect of nationally regulated education and care services To avoid doubt, a provider approval or service approval granted under the National Law Alignment Provisions in respect of a State regulated education and care service is not a provider approval or service approval (as the case requires) for the purposes of the National Law.
